Makro has launched its Easter Sale. The sale will run from 13-19 March 2018, and features a wide range of products on special. Big discounts on electronics, gadgets, appliances, furniture, cameras, office equipment, and, of course, Easter eggs, are available to Makro shoppers. Makro is also running South Africa’s biggest Easter egg hunt, with 72,000 eggs up for grabs and great prizes to be won. “Bring your kids in store,” said Makro, adding that the egg hunt is running from 12 March to 2 April 2018. A selection of great deals from the Makro Easter Sale are shown below.      This article was published in partnership with Makro.